OL,3,CFormer fire chief jailed for
OL,4,Cindecently assaulting teenager
OL,6,FThe former chief of the Northern
OL,7,FIreland Fire and Rescue Service has
OL,8,Fbeen sentenced to eight months in
OL,9,Fprison after pleading guilty to
OL,10,Findecently assaulting a teenager at a
OL,11,Fchurch youth group.
OL,13,FGary Thompson, 56, of Rogan Wood in
OL,14,FNewtownabbey, will also be under
OL,15,Fsupervision for 15 months when he is
OL,16,Freleased.
OL,18,FThe offending was carried out over a
OL,19,Ffour month period in 2006.
