OL,6,FIn a statement, police said "he has
OL,7,Fbeen sentenced today for two counts of
OL,8,Findecent assault against a now 33-year-
OL,9,Fold woman who was only 15-years-old at
OL,10,Fthe time of the abuse. The abuse
OL,11,Foccurred between June and November
OL,12,F2006".
OL,14,FIt added: "He was jailed today at
OL,15,FBelfast Crown Court for eight months
OL,16,Fand probation for 15 months
OL,17,Fthereafter. He will also be subject to
OL,18,Fa five year Sexual Offences Protection
OL,19,FOrder and will be on the sex offenders
OL,20,Fregister for ten years."
