OL,6,FSpeaking out today, Nikella Holmes,
OL,7,Fwho has now waived her right to
OL,8,Fanonymity and spoken out about the
OL,9,Fabuse, released a statement saying: "I
OL,10,Fwould like to thank the PSNI for their
OL,11,Ftremendous work throughout this
OL,12,Flengthy and challenging process. From
OL,13,Fthe moment I reported via 101 I knew I
OL,14,Fwould be treated with respect and
OL,15,Fcare. I was believed and supported,
OL,16,Fthroughout a difficult process by my
OL,17,Finvestigating officer.
