OL,6,F"Predators must face the consequences
OL,7,Fof their actions as my abuser has done
OL,8,Ftoday. I would encourage anyone who
OL,9,Fhas gone through abuse to report if
OL,10,Fthey wish to do so. There is support
OL,11,Ffor you."
OL,13,FDetective Chief Inspector Claire
OL,14,FMcGarvey, said: "Thompson was in a
OL,15,Fposition of trust in the community and
OL,16,Fheld in high regard. He took advantage
OL,17,Fof a 15-year-old child who he
OL,18,Fmanipulated and believed he was in a
OL,19,F'relationship' with.
