OL,6,F"Nikella met Thompson through a
OL,7,FCommunity Church in November 2004. He
OL,8,Fbegan communicating with her over text
OL,9,Fto build a rapport which we would
OL,10,Fclassify as grooming, before
OL,11,Fencouraging in person meet ups in 2006
OL,12,Fwhen the indecent assaults took place
OL,13,Fin his car. He preyed on her and
OL,14,Fthought he would get away with it
OL,15,Fthrough manipulation. He was wrong.
OL,17,F"I'd like to praise Nikella who has
OL,18,Fshown immense bravery and courage in
OL,19,Fsupporting the investigation.
