OL,6,F"We will continue to work around the
OL,7,Fclock to bring child predators before
OL,8,Fthe courts and would encourage anyone
OL,9,Fwho may have been abused in a similar
OL,10,Fway to come forward. The passage of
OL,11,Ftime doesn't matter.
OL,13,F"Child abuse cannot continue in
OL,14,FNorthern Ireland, we will do
OL,15,Feverything in our power to stop
OL,16,Fpredators in their tracks and get
OL,17,Fvictims the justice they deserve."
