OL,6,FGary Thompson was a former Trustee of
OL,7,FExtern, a social justice charity based
OL,8,Fin both Northern Ireland and the
OL,9,FRepublic of Ireland.
OL,11,FIn a statement a spokesperson said:
OL,12,F"Gary Thompson, former Trustee of
OL,13,FExtern Group and Northern Ireland
OL,14,Fboards, was placed on precautionary
OL,15,Fsuspension on 12 December 2018 at the
OL,16,Ftime of the allegations. He was not re-
OL,17,Felected to the Northern Ireland or
OL,18,FGroup boards. Extern takes a zero-
OL,19,Ftolerance approach to any form of
OL,20,Fabuse."
